<opener><lb/><note>Ad Dominum</note> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottum</rs>.
      <lb/><salute>Vir <abbr>Excellme</abbr>, Fautor Honoratissime.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/><rs key="B_1714-06-08_991170515020405501" type="letter">Ex Literis</rs> Tuis ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> meum <date when="1714-06-08">8. Junii</date> datis, et ab illo <date when="1714-07-15">ante triduum</date>
<lb/>demum acceptis magno <subst><del>d</del><add>c</add></subst>um dolore percepi T<subst><del>e</del><add>ibi</add></subst> respons<subst><del>ionem mea </del><add>orias</add></subst> meas
        <lb/><rs key="B_1714-05-15_991170517053905501" type="letters">literas</rs> quas <date when="1714-05-15">15. Maji</date> ad Te miseram nondum redditas esse. Comitabatur has
        <lb/>meas <rs key="B_1714-05-15_991170517053905501" type="letters">literas</rs> <rs type="letters">epistola</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei, qua ut petiisti mentem suam<del> de</del> num
                    <lb/><abbr>scil.</abbr> acceptaturus esset<del> vocationem</del> <rs type="organisation">cathedram <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinam</rs></rs> sibi ab <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr>
<lb/><rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>i <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs></rs> <abbr>DD.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs> offerendam Tibi aperuit, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> huc
         <lb/>redit, statum nempe rei su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> domestic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ob numerosam et amplam familiam
                    <lb/>aliaque obstacula non levia<subst><del>impedire quominus vocationem</del><add>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non</add></subst> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non nisi insigni fortun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>melioratione bonorumque augmentatione amoveri possint, impedire quo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>minus vocationi a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>uere posset. Idem respondit <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119291967" type="person">Abbati Fardell<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/>in <rs type="letter">literis</rs><note type="comment">Dieser Brief von Fardella ist nicht erhalten.</note><del>dudum</del> jam pridem ad ipsum scriptis, quarum excerptum <add>in</add> eadem
        <lb/><add>mea</add> <rs key="B_1714-05-15_991170517053905501" type="letters">epistola</rs> <date when="1714-05-15">15. Maji</date> ad Te data Tibi transmiseram, simulque <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119291967" type="person">Abbatem</rs>
        <lb/>rogavit ut quia <add>salva</add> modestia tam lautum stipendium ab <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Refor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mator<add>ibus</add></rs> <add>pro se</add> petere non ausit, animum ab hoc proposito abduc<subst><del><unclear>et</unclear></del><add>eret</add></subst>, et<del> quod</del> potius
        <lb/>id quod habe<del>n</del>t auctoritatis apud <abbr>Illmos</abbr> Vestros <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Proceres</rs> adhibe<subst><del>nt</del><add>ret</add></subst> ad spart<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>hanc mihi procurandam. Ego vero, qui honori <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs></rs>
<lb/>optime consultum vellem et proinde vehementer optarem ut <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs>
<lb/>meus petitioni <add>vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> locum daret, in dicta mea <rs key="B_1714-05-15_991170517053905501" type="letter">epistola</rs> subjunxi, quod putem ob<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stacula h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c amotum iri stipendio <subst><del>honorifico</del><add>annuo</add></subst> 1500<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> thaleros nostrates cir<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citer <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quante,<del> mihi etenim persuadeo</del> quam su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am si <abbr>Illmi</abbr> et <abbr>Excellmi</abbr>
        <lb/>Domini <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> meo offerant, negotium ex voto successu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum credo;<del> <unclear>in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim</unclear> quoque si</del> quo casu tamen opus etiam erit
                    <lb/>consensu <rs type="organisation">Magistratus</rs> nostri,<del> ad</del> quem proin <abbr>Illmi</abbr> et <abbr>Excllmi</abbr>
<lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs><del> lit</del> <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> quadam rogare deberent, ut <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs>
<pb facs="1038305" n="131v"/>
<lb/>meo permittat in paucos annos <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> <subst><del><gap/></del><add>dis</add></subst>cedere Matheseos docend<unclear>i</unclear>
<lb/>gratia. Si vero existimes inutiliter h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c proponi <abbr>Illmis</abbr> et <abbr>Excllmis</abbr>
<lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs>, gratum mihi erit quodcunque mei gratia <add>porro</add> facies.
            <lb/><rs key="biblio_WPXENY2H biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblios">Fasciculum</rs> continentem <rs key="biblio_WPXENY2H" type="biblio">Artem Conjectandi</rs>, <rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2" type="biblio"><choice><orig>dissertationem</orig><reg>Dissertationem</reg></choice> de fer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mentatione et effervescentia</rs>, <rs key="biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">Essai d'une Nouvelle Theorie <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr>,
                    <lb/>et Essai d'Analyse sur les Jeux de Hazard</rs> mittam <add><rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergom<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs></add> ad <abbr>Illmum</abbr> et
        <lb/><abbr>Excllm<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr> <abbr>Dnum</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089631200" type="person">Carolum Zenobium</rs>, quamprimum exemplaria
            <lb/><rs key="biblios_WPXENY2H biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">posterioris libri</rs><del> expecto</del> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quotidie expecto acceper<subst><del><gap/></del><add>o</add></subst>.
        <lb/>Poteris si lubet <rs type="letters" key="B_1712-06-02_991170517023705501 B_1712-10-11_991170517023405501 B_1712-12-30_991170517023205501 B_1713-01-23_991170430192305501 B_1713-09-09_991170517022605501">literas</rs> meas hoc <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46" type="biblio">libro</rs><note type="comment">In Monmorts zweiter Auflage des Essay d'analyse sur les jeux de hazard sind mehrere Briefe Niclaus I Bernoullis im Anhang aufgeführt.</note> contentas loco speciminis
            <lb/>ostendere <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Excll.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatorib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice></rs> tantisper dum Dissertatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem<subst><del> mihi</del><add>aliquam</add></subst>  conscribere mihi liceat. Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de Problematibus mihi propositis
         <lb/>de velocitate fluidi per canales ramosos moti, de fluidorum
         <lb/>pressionibus perpendicularibus ad superficies continentes, et de
        <lb/>regula generali <rs key="biblio_WPXENY2H" type="biblio">Artis Conjectandi</rs> in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicta mea <rs key="B_1714-05-15_991170517053905501" type="letters">epistola</rs>
<lb/>dixi nunc non attingo, ne diutius differam hanc responsionem, quam
                    <lb/>hac vice per aliam viam quam per <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergamum</rs> mitto, quia
         <lb/>ut video nescio an ob negligentiam cursorum an aliam ob caus<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
         <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c via minus tuta est. Poteris inposterum si lubet literas Tuas
              <lb/>per eandem viam mittere, per quam ut spero citius et tutius ibunt.</p>
<closer><lb/><salute>Vale et fave</salute> <abbr>Excllmi</abbr> Nominis Tui Cultori humillimo <signed><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>N. B.</abbr></rs></signed> <dateline><date when="1714-07-18">18. Julij 1714</date></dateline><supplied>.</supplied></closer>
